<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98843078846675></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98843078846675><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=7&mid=98843078846675>RE: what is the best race for a cleric?</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=7&mid=98843078846675#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=51744><span id= >Eberk</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>5 posts</td></tr>
