	   <tr><td colspan=2>I too am twinking a Cleric.&nbsp;&nbsp;Some things I have found for my level 10 DE Cleric.<br><br>Velium Etched Stone Mace 7/22 +3 STR +3 WIS get it from the named Tizmak in Great Divid, you can get it at level 32 with your Pali and a group.  While your there you will get almost a full set of Tizmak Armor Arms and legs are 8AC and 3 wt, very nice and if you get lucky the cured tunic is 15 AC and gloves are 9AC and the look is unique.<br><br>I wear 1 moonstone ring (50pp or so) +3 str +30 mana and use the Skull of Jen'tra for the 20 mana.  I just went and got a Runed Circlet from Permafrost 5AC +4 wis, they sell for about 50pp too, but again your Pali could just go get 1.  While in Permafrost you might try for the Mamoth Hide Cape but thats usually camped 24/7.<br><br>Chakor,<br>   What are the stats on the bloodstone rings and how much should I pay for them?  And what do you recommend for earrings?  I can't afford Forest loops and can't stand to fight in Fronteer Mts long enough to get 2 drops.  Are Polished Bone Hoops the best bet at this level (+10 mana)?  And what is the best bet for the wrist slots?<br><br>Vildaar<br>lvl 10 DE Cleric<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
